    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We do not have children inside an `option` because the HTML doesn't support this behaviour. The only type of content allowed in an `option` element is a [Text](https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/form-elements.html#the-option-element) node.\r\n\r\nBut you can implement your own widget with the [`connectMenu`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectMenu.html) connector. The connector API lets you have the full control on the rendering of your widgets. You can find more information about that [in the documentation](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/guides/customization.html).",
